token_info.name: High Cross
token_info.description: a classic Brazilian tradition is to place a cross on the highest point of the cemetery to be placed offerings like flowers and candles to help guide the spirits to the beyond, with that I leave this cross here so we can place our beliefs and offerings to help the dead to your trip, and when our time comes that this cross can help us to be guided - photogrammetry made with more than 2000.jpeg / 2021 Higor Casagrande
